Sentencas: A ceramic ceria gadolinia solid solution membrane for solid oxide, fuel cells was fabricated by tape casting using a nanopowder of 37 nm average particle size.
Titulo: Tape casting of nanocrystalline ceria gadolinia powder

Sentencas: A novel combination of solvent and dispersant was used to disperse the nanoparticles.

Sentencas: The polymer was added in a dilute stage to guarantee a homogeneous distribution.
Titulo: Tape casting of nanocrystalline ceria gadolinia powder

Sentencas: After casting a remarkable densification of the cast tape suspension from a solid loading of 20 up to 42 vol.% was observed during drying.
Titulo: Tape casting of nanocrystalline ceria gadolinia powder

Sentencas: The green tape was sintered to >92% theoretical density and was dense towards perfusion.
Titulo: Tape casting of nanocrystalline ceria gadolinia powder
